node.text:
#ad I’m very excited to share @narwalrobot with you. Narwal is the World’s 1st self-cleaning robot mop and vacuum. It’s really the best #cleaninghack this mama has found yet! You can remotely control the robot with the App from anywhere. Click the link in my bio to pre-order now with $1 to save $180 on June 1. The #narwalt10 is so intelligent that it separates paths for sweeping and mopping. It’s really amazing because it automatically detects when the mop heads are dirty too. The #robot will return to the station for cleaning and drying. Once clean the robot restarts the task. Narwal is absolutely terrific at maneuvering from floor to carpet, under, and between furniture. I’m so impressed at how well this #robotvacuum sweeps and mops my home. Narwal allows me more free time to spend with the family. You should definitely check it out by clicking the link in my bio. #robotmop 
🧹🤖🧹🤖

node.text:
#ad Radio Flyer’s Ultimate Go-Kart is a HUGE hit in our neighborhood! We hosted a really fun test drive party. All the kiddos gave it two thumbs up and five stars ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️!! Even the teenagers came around to check it out. 
Give your kiddos the gift of hours of exciting outdoor play and #unwrapradioflyer this Holiday season. 🎁 🏎 
The awesome electric car from @radioflyerinc can be plugged in to recharge and runs for hours! The #radioflyer Ultimate Go-Kart  has so many wonderful safety features, including a sturdy steel frame. Kiddos will stay safe with the parent-controlled speed lock, seat belt, and cool high-visibility racing flag. There are large rear wheels and great rubber traction.  It’s perfect for kiddos ages 3-8 and holds up to 81 pounds. The car can be set at 2.5 , 5, and 8 mph. It has single speed reverse.  Both boys are having a blast racing each other and driving around.  This is #kidapproved and a definite #momwin. Check it out for the kiddos on your list and give them the ULTIMATE Holiday gift.🎁 You can find it at https://www.radioflyer.com and 
https://www.walmart.com 🏎

node.text:
(Ad) Check out my Top Picks for stocking stuffers and holiday gifts for the kiddos on your list from @mywikkistix.  Wikki Stix are an #ecofriendly toy and a craft in one! You can reuse them over and over.  They can be bent, cut, twisted, and so much more. No glue needed and they are mess free crafting. There are so many fun engaging learning activities and crafts kiddos of all ages can create. Give the kids on your list the gift this holiday that sparks their imaginations and keeps them busy creating for hours! 
https://www.wikkistix.com 🎁

node.text:
https://www.target.com/s?searchTerm=stomp+rocket (Ad) Get your kiddos outside and active with the @theoriginalstomprocket from @target. This makes a fantastic holiday gift for ages 5 and up. We received the Stomp Rocket Stunt Planes High Flying Planes with Launch Pad 3pk.  https://www.target.com/s?searchTerm=stomp+rocket 🚀
Dominic and Scotty are having a blast stomping, jumping, and running to launch the rockets.  Active play is so important for kids. Having them participate in #unpluggedplay is beneficial for their overall development. This toy combines working on #stemlearning and #grossmotorskills all while having a great time! 🚀
I love that the Stomp Rocket 🚀 has kiddos using their brain and muscle power. The boys are having a lot of fun trying to launch the rocket at different angles, into a box, and the basketball hoop. It’s great watching the boys thinking, discussing, and trying new ideas with this toy. As a mom and early childhood educator this is the type of toy I get excited about! 🚀

node.text: I absolutely love our new #Enlite10 candles by @cr8vproducts and so do the boys!  This #environmentallyconscious company is owned and ran by all woman. The candles provide a sustainable source of light by using a solar panel to charge the rechargeable batteries. The candles look gorgeous from the exterior and interior. I leave them on my windows and the sun does all the work! I am using them as night lights in multiple rooms including my kitchen and the boys rooms. It automatically turns on during the night and off during the day. Being a single mama I am going non stop all day and this is one less thing to worry about. Also, I love that they are environmentally friendly 💚 because every little bit counts. #ad #Crv8Products

node.text:
#sponsored Did you know August is National Wellness Month?

This month long event is to promote self-care, stress management, and healthy routines. I like getting readings and often look for psychic guidance in my life. Keen @keenpsychics is committed to supporting universal spiritual health through access to spiritual advisors. I love how they view wellness as a holistic approach to health which encompasses the body, mind, and spirit. 

Keen has the largest network of advisors to guide you and help you find answers on your spiritual journey. It’s so easy to get an online reading and I always feel more grounded and relaxed after. 

It’s so important to take time for yourself everyday. We all need to de-stress, recharge, and relax. There are so many ways to incorporate healthy habits into your daily wellness routine. Take a bubble bath, read, relax outside, walk, or do yoga. August is the perfect time to make some changes to form a healthier lifestyle. Whether you need clarity about relationships, career, or finance the psychics at Keen are there to guide you. 🔮✨

Click the link in my bio or below and get the first 3 minutes of your first reading for free! Then head over to Keen's @keenpsychics Instagram for special giveaways and wellness tips all throughout the month of August. #keenpsychics #nationalwellnessmonth #hbtkeenwellness 
🔮✨🔮✨

We gave him the nickname “snuggles” and of course Scotty soon after he was born. Recently Scott stopped kissing me but still gives me hugs. It makes me sad but I knew it coming because it happened with Dom even earlier than age 7. 

He lost his first front tooth about two weeks ago and was super excited. I often feel like time is robbing me. I want to freeze moments and go back to the baby stage. It seems like I blinked and he is starting 2nd grade. 
Do your kids or you have nicknames?

node.text:
Thank you @skeeterhawkusa for sending us this awesome #allnatural bundle to keep the mosquitoes away while #outdoors! Spending Friday swimming and relaxing at Nonna’s (that’s my mom in the pool). We are now able to enjoy all of our favorite activities like hikes, picnics, soccer, pool, and playgrounds without getting tons of bites. Our bundle includes the Personal Mosquito Zapper & Lantern, Handheld Mosquito Racket, Wearable Mosquito Wrist Band, Wearable Mosquito Carabiner, and 3 Packs of Repellent Tabs. 

We definitely will be using these all year long here in South Carolina. I really like that they are effective, all natural, and don’t contain nasty harsh chemicals. Also, they are totally safe for the whole family including pets and kids. I’m so glad we don’t need to use smelly bug sprays anymore. We still were getting bites with the sprays but not with the #skeeterhawk products.  #guardyouryard #pestdefense #bugseason 
🌿🌴🌿🌴

(Ad) We are gearing up for back to school with some awesome #STEM activities using @mywikkistix! This afternoon the boys are creating the molecular structure of water using the Wikki Stix STEM Pak and poster board. This is really a fun and simple #STEAMlearning activity. Just shape, stick, and create! 

The STEM Pak is 108 feet of reusable #wikkistix in 9 colors. Each one is 3 feet long! Also, it includes 20 additional projects and a QR code to scan for more ideas. 

Remember you can cut, twist, shape, and bend, any way you want. They are safe for everyone and free from oil, nuts, latex, and gluten. Wikki Stix are made in the USA from yarn and food grade wax. 

Find this and more educational activities on the #wikkistix website. Click this link in my bio⬇️

https://www.wikkistix.com/product/stem-pak/

(Ad) Your kiddos can embark on an artistic adventure at home with an awesome themed art box from @artropiaforkids. Each box includes all materials needed, a theme, 4 projects, supplies, and an adventure story. Scotty really is enjoying creating his own pet Alebrijes and more with this box. There is an accompanying App with Brodi the Bear that kiddos can use while creating. It’s so immersive and fun. Scotty is already asking for another box! The App and Brodi the Bear help kids by using theme based teaching methods developed by educators and artists. Just downloaded the App in the App Store or Google Play when you receive your box and #getcrafty. 

As you all know we absolutely love creating and doing different art projects in our home. We received the Mythical Creatures them to make a dragon, unicorn, mermaid flip book, and pet Alebrijes. This box is wonderful because the price includes everything you need to make the projects. Each box focuses on themed based learning by global awareness, creative expression, and critical thinking. I really like that kiddos are working on building artistic skills, creativity, and critical thinking skills doing these theme based projects. 

Also, kiddos can be as imaginative as they want and mix project pieces to come up with their own creations too! Scotty is so proud of his artistic accomplishments using these materials to create. He spent hours really concentrating and planning his creation. He specifically picked certain colors and decorations for each part. Even after he thought he was all done he decided to add a smile and nose to his Pet Alebrijes. This box sparks kiddos imaginations and gives them the tools they need to feel a sense of accomplishment. These are the types of activities where kiddos are learning without even knowing it because they are having a blast!!! I highly recommend checking out this awesome themed art box with the accompanying App from @artropiaforkids. 
Get your first Artropia box 30% using the link below. 

https://www.artropia.com/pay/10001?channelId=1013

#Artropia #Artropiaforkids #STEAM #STEM #themedbox #Arteducation #artplay #learningthroughplay #Designthinking #Creative #Adventurestory

#ad This year we are making Dominic’s 9th birthday extra memorable with a personalized book from Starring You Books by Jib Jab @starringyoubooks. It’s a family tradition for the boys to pick a book to give to each on their birthday. Creating and gifting the story is such an enjoyable heartwarming experience. You get to personalize the book with the gift giver and receiver’s faces! Plus, there are over 100 custom pages to pick from that include different themes of hobbies and activities. Starring You Books by Jib Jab are high quality hardcover books that will become a treasured keepsake. They come in a variety of book covers to pick from too. These books are a wonderful opportunity to get a personalized gift for your loved one’s birthday. As you can see from Dominic’s face he loves being the star! 

Scotty and I had a blast making this unique, colorful, silly, and personalized story for Dominic. These books are really special and will bring a huge smile to the giver and recipient. Starring You Books by Jib Jab make a unique gifting option for the entire family. I am so impressed with the quality and ease of creating the book, that I will be buying one for Scotty’s birthday as well as gifts from the boys to their grandparents. 

Get your book at http://starringyoubooks.com/ and use code 28off for 28% off your order. 📚#StarringYouBooks

#ad Halloween 🎃 is the boys favorite holiday. We so excited to introduce you to Jabberin’ Jack from @mindscopeproducts. This #halloweendecor is so cool and fun!Jabberin’ Jack has a built in projector and comes with a USB cable to plug in. There is over 70 minutes of talking, singing, and joking. He is a traditional, spooky, and funny jack-o-lantern all in one. The three different types of animation are really awesome and entertaining to watch. Also, you can choose to keep him silent and just light up. The volume and Halloween moods are easily controlled by buttons on the top of the #jackolantern. 

This #Halloween decor is made for indoor use or a covered porch and is not waterproof. Last year #JabberinJack $59.99 sold out online in August so hurry and grab one soon! 

https://mindscopeproducts.com/pages/jabberinjack 

🎃🎃🎃🎃 @kidstuff.pr
